{"id":"262445010_Proposal_for_Measuring_the_Impact_of_ICT_on_College_Teaching","abstract":"The general objective of this article is to define at an appropriate method for measuring the impact of ICT on teaching-learning processes in higher education (IMPACTIC). In terms of its context, the study is centered on faculties in the area of humanities. The construction of IMPACTIC is related to the basics, particularly an analysis of teaching models, processes for incorporating ICT into educational contexts, and the impact of technology on the educational environment.","authors":["Gloria Patricia Ávila-Fajardo","Sandra Cristina Riascos Erazo"],"meta":["April 2011Educación y Educadores 14(1):169-188","DOI:10.5294/edu.2011.14.1.9"],"references":["341505540_Construccion_de_un_instrumento_para_la_evaluacion_de_las_estrategias_de_ensenanza_de_cursos_telematicos_de_formacion_universitaria","277263594_Evolucion_del_modelo_docente_efectos_de_la_incorporacion_del_uso_de_una_plataforma_virtual_videos_educativos_y_CD_interactivos","247813294_The_Competent_Manager_A_Model_For_Effective_Performance","44837273_Monitoring_and_Evaluation_of_ICT_in_Education_Projects_A_Handbook_for_Developing_Countries","28149587_Virtual_base_para_el_desarrollo_de_la_competencia_pedagogica_de_uso_de_la_tecnologia_en_la_formacion_de_profesores","28090414_El_trabajo_colaborativo_en_situaciones_no_presenciales","26496454_Desarrollo_de_competencias_mediante_Blended_Learning_Un_analisis_descriptivo","285929431_A_framework_for_understanding_and_evaluating_the_impact_of_information_and_communication_technologies_in_education","228584349_MANUAL_PARA_LA_EVALUACION_DE_IMPACTO_EN_PROGRAMAS_DE_FORMACION_PARA_JOVENES"]}